<BlogLayout
  title="Words Starting with POST in Scrabble"
  description="Complete list of valid POST- words in Scrabble sorted by length. Strategy for using POST prefix words to hit premium squares and score bingo bonuses. Free."
  keywords="post words scrabble, words starting with post, post prefix scrabble, postmark scrabble, postpone scrabble, scrabble post words list, bingo words scrabble"
>
  <script type="application/ld+json" set:html={JSON.stringify({
    "@context": "https://schema.org",
    "@type": "Article",
    "headline": "Words Starting with POST in Scrabble",
    "description": "Complete list of valid POST- words in Scrabble with strategy for using timing-related prefix words to earn bingo bonuses.",
    "datePublished": "2026-06-20",
    "dateModified": "2026-07-04",
    "author": { "@type": "Person", "name": "Raj Naik", "url": "https://www.scrabblewordsfinder.com/about/" },
    "publisher": { "@type": "Organization", "name": "ScrabbleWordsFinder.com" },
    "mainEntityOfPage": { "@type": "WebPage", "@id": "https://www.scrabblewordsfinder.com/blog/words-starting-with-post" }
  })} />

  <script type="application/ld+json" set:html={JSON.stringify({
    "@context": "https://schema.org",
    "@type": "FAQPage",
    "mainEntity": [
      {
        "@type": "Question",
        "name": "How many words starting with POST are valid in Scrabble?",
        "acceptedAnswer": { "@type": "Answer", "text": "There are approximately 80+ valid POST- words in the TWL and SOWPODS dictionaries combined. These range from 4 letters (POST itself is valid, worth 6 points) to 12+ letters. SOWPODS accepts additional POST- words. The prefix is especially valuable because POST is a common standalone word that can be extended on subsequent turns." }
      },
      {
        "@type": "Question",
        "name": "What are the best POST words for scoring in Scrabble?",
        "acceptedAnswer": { "@type": "Answer", "text": "The highest-scoring common POST words include POSTFIX (19 points base), POSTBOX (18 points), and POSTMARK (16 points). For bingo plays, 8-letter POST words like POSTPONE (12+50), POSTCARD (13+50), and POSTMARK (16+50) are most valuable. POST itself at 6 points is a solid setup play that enables future extensions." }
      },
      {
        "@type": "Question",
        "name": "Can POST be played as a word by itself in Scrabble?",
        "acceptedAnswer": { "@type": "Answer", "text": "Yes! POST is valid in both TWL and SOWPODS as a standalone word worth 6 points. It can function as a noun, verb, or adjective. This makes POST an excellent setup play — you can drop it early and extend it into POSTS, POSTED, POSTER, POSTAL, POSTMAN, or POSTPONE on later turns for significantly higher scores." }
      }
    ]
  })} />

  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 pt-4 pb-12">
