<h2 class="text-xl font-light text-amber-600 dark:text-amber-400 mt-10 mb-4 border-l-4 border-amber-400 pl-4">Sharpen Your Skills</h2>

<div class="not-prose my-6 grid grid-cols-1 gap-4">
